    <abstract>
      <t>   This document specifies procedures to automatically establish context
   based forwarding for providing fast reroute during egress node and
   egress link failures.  It describes how to detect multi-homed
   services and establish context for forwarding.  It also defines
   procedures to avoid conflicts among routers while establishing
   context.


	 </t>
